Thats correct. With only Elemental Fury and Speed of Salik for damage enhancing buffs my Water pet did 24572 damage in 2mins 24seconds to Ptav Msha on last Sunday. That works out at 170.64 dps. Thats melee damage only not including any proc damage (and no epic as a) I don't have it and b) it wouldn't land on Msha anyway).
<br />

<br />
Against Iqthinxa (just Iqthinxa herself after the 3 animals dead) Water pet did 33476 damage in 3 min 24secs (164.1 dps). Did have a bard for part of this fight (wasn't getting the overhaste song for all of it) but pet did not get back of mob for entire fight (did for most of it though). Only damage enchancing buff I remember having was Elemental Fury + the bard songs when they hit me/pet (yes bard slacked!)
<br />

<br />
For those interested I did 505 and 580 dps total respectively in the 2 fights mentioned above (not including animals in Iqthinxa fight). Thats using Blade Strike for nukes as you cannot use Fire on Qvic goat models.
<br />

<br />
Was going to parse more Msha on Monday but I was heavily lagged when we killed them so it was worthless trying to log damage.
<br />

<br />
